public record User(int userId, String userName, String password, Timestamp createDate, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdateBy) extends Record
A data carrier class that contains database CRUD operations as static methods for the users table. A row returned from the table is packaged as a User data-transfer-like object.
